{"type":"message","id":"6ff6ec47","parentId":"6d7adb7d","timestamp":"2026-04-27T16:04:39.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze:\n\nGmail - 5 new emails:\n1. Affirm - \"Important notification about your prequalification request\" - might be important/promotion\n2. Angelina Auchmoody - Apartments.com network lead - IMPORTANT (personal/business)\n3. PetScreening - \"Non-Compliant Pet: Immediate Action Needed\" - URGENT ⚠️\n4. Epidemic Sound - \"50% off!\" - LOW PRIORITY (promotion)\n5. Affirm - \"An update on your Affirm Application\" - IMPORTANT\n\niCloud - 3 emails:\n- ID 8: Re: Looking for new apartment from RC Leasing (2026-04-27 12:20) - Flags empty, so not read - IMPORTANT\n\n\n- ID 7 and 6 are both marked as read, so I can skip those\n\nNow I'll draft the Gmail message first with the Urgent category showing PetScreening as the only item, then move to Important where I have Affirm prequalification, Angelina's Apartments.com lead, and the Affirm application update, and finish with the Low Priority section for the Epidemic Sound promotion.\n\nFor iCloud, there's just one new message from RC Leasing about an apartment inquiry, so that goes into Important.\n\nI'll send the Gmail report now.\n","thinkingSignature":"ffc4d3afc5874adf939b899cd438f721b92b374bcdd6b42371d81defa3dc1af3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h883pkbbcwno_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","message":"📬 GMAIL — New Mail (5 new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• PetScreening — Non-Compliant Pet: Immediate Action Needed\n  └ ⚠️ Action needed on a pet — please review immediately\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• Affirm — Important notification about your prequalification request\n  └ You may have been prequalified for Affirm financing\n• Angelina Auchmoody — RE: Apartments.com Network lead for The Union Street Historic District\n  └ New lead from WalkWay Realty on a property listing\n• Affirm — An update on your Affirm Application\n  └ Status update on your Affirm financing application\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• Epidemic Sound — Level up your content: 50% off!\n  └ Limited-time deal on Epidemic Sound subscription","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":596,"output":493,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777305865407,"responseId":"063ebc09fabbe41570c38832592df99b"}}
