{"type":"message","id":"38d91e70","parentId":"124370b4","timestamp":"2026-04-27T16:04:53.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Both emails checked and sent. Gmail had 5 new emails (1 urgent, 3 important, 1 low priority). iCloud had 1 new important email from RC Leasing about the apartment application.\n","thinkingSignature":"56ce49e96363d67248295a5058ca2daec9d3febd1e34e1afffa5f03a1b98254d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBoth emails sent. Here's the summary:\n\n**Gmail (5 new):**\n- 🔴 PetScreening — Non-Compliant Pet (action needed)\n- 🟡 2x Affirm (prequalification & application update)\n- 🟡 Angelina (Apartments.com lead for Union Street Historic District)\n- ⚪ Epidemic Sound 50% off\n\n**iCloud (1 new):**\n- 🟡 RC Leasing — asking when you want to move so they can confirm unit availability (waiting on Logan's application)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":158,"output":158,"cacheRead":20864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21180,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777305887836,"responseId":"063ebc1f72f1f63b3946f0d148e468d0"}}
